<h4><a href="https://www.jiemian.com/article/5243328.html">伊利申请「牛 YEAR」、「嗨皮牛夜」商标</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1377879" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/160490987494370800_a700xH.png" alt="" width="700" height="428" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/160490987494370800_a700xH.png 700w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/160490987494370800_a700xH-360x220.png 360w" sizes="(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" /></p>
<p>天眼查 app 显示内蒙古伊利实业集团股份有限公司申请多条「牛 YEAR」、「嗨皮牛夜」商标，国际分类涉及方便食品、食品、医药、啤酒饮料等，状态为商标申请中。</p>
<h4><a href="https://www.jiemian.com/article/5242937.html">北京严打以「结婚」为手段过户京牌</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1367459" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/japanese-marriage-agency-marriage-matching.jpg" alt="" width="1600" height="1067" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/japanese-marriage-agency-marriage-matching.jpg 1600w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/japanese-marriage-agency-marriage-matching-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/japanese-marriage-agency-marriage-matching-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/japanese-marriage-agency-marriage-matching-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px" /></p>
<p>据北京日报报道，今年以来，以「结婚」为手段过户京牌指标违法犯罪持续高发，严重破坏社会管理秩序，北京警方依托「平安 3 号行动」对此开展打击整治。通过八天连续作战，截至 11 月 6 日，共抓获嫌疑人 166 人，其中 124 人以结婚为手段骗取、买卖北京市小客车指标的违法犯罪行为，因涉嫌买卖国家机关公文罪已被公安机关依法刑事拘留。</p>
<h4><a href="https://www.jiemian.com/article/5242318.html">超 56 万韩国 5G 用户重返 4G：不满 5G 速度和运营商服务</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1375908" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/5g8.jpg" alt="" width="4752" height="3168" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/5g8.jpg 4752w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/5g8-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/5g8-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/5g8-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 4752px) 100vw, 4752px" /></p>
<p>据日经亚洲评论报道，近日韩国广播和通信委员会成员洪贞敏表示，因消费者对 5G 质量低劣、覆盖范围不足和收费高昂不满，有多达 562656 人已从 5G 切换回 4G 服务，占韩国三家国内移动运营商 5G 用户总数的 6.5% 之多。</p>
<h4><a href="https://china.kyodonews.net/news/2020/11/1fd7b8f6110c.html?phrase=%E4%BC%98%E8%A1%A3%E5%BA%93&amp;words=%E4%BC%98,%E8%A1%A3,%E5%BA%93">优衣库门店建筑物等首次申请外观设计专利</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1377994" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/photo_l.jpg" alt="" width="960" height="609" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/photo_l.jpg 960w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/photo_l-360x228.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/photo_l-768x487.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px" /></p>
<div class="editor-image-source">
<p>▲ 图片来自：共同社</p>
</div>
<p>据共同社报道，日本特许厅日前发布消息称，休闲服饰品牌「优衣库」的门店及东日本铁路公司（JR 东日本）的车站外观设计等已获得注册。为保护企业品牌价值，基于修订版《意匠法》（或称《外观设计法》），「建筑物」「图像」「内部装潢」等从 4 月 1 日起也成为保护对象，此次的一系列注册均属首次。</p>
<p>作为建筑物注册的是横滨市的「优衣库 PARK 横滨湾畔店」，该店外观呈阶梯状，室外空间可供休息和游玩。</p>
<h4><a href="https://hypebeast.com/2020/11/vf-corp-supreme-acquisition">Supreme 被 Timberland 母公司收购，作价超 21 亿美元</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1377995" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/https___hypebeast.com_image_2020_11_vf-corp-supreme-acquisition-1.jpg" alt="" width="1238" height="826" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/https___hypebeast.com_image_2020_11_vf-corp-supreme-acquisition-1.jpg 1238w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/https___hypebeast.com_image_2020_11_vf-corp-supreme-acquisition-1-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/https___hypebeast.com_image_2020_11_vf-corp-supreme-acquisition-1-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/https___hypebeast.com_image_2020_11_vf-corp-supreme-acquisition-1-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1238px) 100vw, 1238px" /></p>
<p>据 Hypebeast 报道，知名街头品牌 Supreme 被 Vans、Timberland 以及 The North Face 等品牌的母公司 VF Corporation（威富集团）以超 21 亿美元的价格收购。Supreme 创始人 James Jebbia 对媒体回应称，收购完成后 Supreme 仍将保持独立性。</p>
<h3><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1293890" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo.png" alt="" width="1029" height="180" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo.png 1029w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo-360x63.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo-768x134.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo-1024x179.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1029px) 100vw, 1029px" /></h3>
<h4><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/2151481347/4569309035106003">凡尔赛文学</a></h4>
<p>一句话介绍凡尔赛文学，那就是在社交平台用看似平和的文字，不经意间流露出自己的优越感。凡尔赛文学的作者需要被仰慕吹捧的虚荣感，而社交平台的用户也需要一个偶像，双方都获得了自己想要的东西。</p>
<p>网友：「半夜弹钢琴玩乐器，网友说注意点会吵到邻居，我说我没有邻居毕竟独栋别墅不会吵到别人！我说是凡尔赛文学，周杰伦说是纪实文学。」「顶级凡尔赛：我对钱没有兴趣！」「尿（sui）性。」</p>
<h3><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1357580" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/wed.png" alt="" width="1029" height="165" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/wed.png 1029w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/wed-360x58.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/wed-768x123.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/wed-1024x164.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1029px) 100vw, 1029px" /></h3>
<h4><a href="https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/Rgqs_LCssWOeThA3o06AAQ">动画大电影《海绵宝宝：营救大冒险》</a></h4>
<p>11 月 6 日，派拉蒙动画大电影《海绵宝宝：营救大冒险》上线了国内平台，通过单片付费（会员 6 元、非会员 12 元）的方式给海绵宝宝的粉丝们提供了一个新的观看渠道。作为全球知名 IP，海绵宝宝在 80 后、90 后观众的记忆里都留下了深刻印象，而大电影中的种种场景也都能让你回忆童年。</p>
<p>生活在海里（摸鱼）的海绵宝宝总能给平静的世界制造麻烦，但他也一直能摆脱困境，试问「打工人」们如何不羡慕呢？</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1377673" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/p2624711667.jpg" alt="" width="1280" height="688" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/p2624711667.jpg 1280w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/p2624711667-360x194.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/p2624711667-768x413.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/p2624711667-1024x550.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px" /></p>
<div id="ifanr_profile" style="border:1px solid #ccc;font-size:14px;margin:27px auto;font-family:Arial;">
<div style="overflow:hidden"><a target="_blank" href="https://www.ifanr.com/author/lengsizhen" style="color:#000;text-decoration:none;"></a>
<div style="text-align:left;line-height:23px;margin-left:80px">
